description:
In Frogs vs. Storks you play with little frogs that make a good and peaceful living in their beautiful pond. But, with the arrival of storks, the pond became a dangerous place to live! Storks are everywhere now just waiting for their chance to eat the frogs!
Outsmart evil storks and once again make the pond a peaceful place to live in Frogs vs. Storks.

- 5 stages increasing difficulty 
- 5 different achievements
- 40 unique levels and hours of fun and challenge
- Create your own levels with LEVEL GENERATOR and enjoy the unlimited fun!
- Dare to win all achievements and high-score on most challenging stages
name: Frogs vs. Storks
intro: Save your frogs from evil storks and make the pond a peaceful place to live!
